ld significant\npotential for coding theoretic constructions and view this work as\ndemonstrating the power of double samplers in this context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2018 17:10:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 13:15:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
