aev-Heisenberg model on the\nhyperhoneycomb lattice. Our results are in excellent agreement with previous\nstudies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Aug 2018 06:05:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2018 04:09:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Feb 2019 14:41:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-08"}
