h a neural\nnetwork to obtain a score for the headline. We test our model over 2538 posts\n(having trained it on 17000 records) and achieve an accuracy of 83.49%\noutscoring previous state-of-the-art approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Aug 2018 09:02:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-06"}
